main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Overton, Nevada on June 25, 1965, at 2333 hours.
interesting points: The object was observed for an interrupted period and was described as having bright illumination and hovering,It was estimated to have been traveling at a speed of 600 mph heading southwest,The report suggests the sighting might have been an upper air research balloon bursting,The experience left the witness feeling a sense of dread and unease,The object was described as approximately 75-80 feet in diameter and hovered at an altitude of about 800 feet.
sighted object: an unidentified object with bright illumination
witness description: The witness provided many details about the object, its movement, and experienced a profound sense of unease.
